parameters: Banka: "Let's stay at this inn tonight."
Kru: "It seems there are only single rooms available."

Banka: "Yes. So, everyone will have separate rooms. Aren't you going to be
lonely, Umi-san?"

Shopkeeper: "Please, customer... spare me. Your moaning last night was
incredible."

Banka: "Ah, my bad, my bad. The prostitute last night was just so lewd and
wild!"
Shopkeeper: "Please spare me. This isn't a brothel, you know."
Shopkeeper: "And please, ask the same of your companion."
Kru: "Umi... you have bags under your eyes. Didn't sleep well?"

Banka: "Ah, sorry about that. It must've been because of the noisy woman I
brought back, right?"
Kru: "Really... where do you pick up such indecent and lewd women?"

Banka: "Ah... she was a fine woman. Her heart and body were both utterly
lewd."

Kru: "Umi... if the journey is tough, just say so. There's no need to rush
back."
